The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 UN honour for India, Pak

United Nations: The United Nations has formally appointed the national cricket teams of India and Pakistan as spokespersons for the International Year of Sport and Physical Education, 2005. This decision has been taken in recognition of the outstanding example both have set in overcoming regional tensions. (PTI) 




